# satip-lab core context

Read `AGENTS.md` at repo root before making changes.

- **English only** for docs, comments, commits, PRs, and agent replies (US spelling preferred).
- Don’t assume. Don’t hide confusion. Surface tradeoffs.
- Minimum code that solves the problem. Nothing speculative.
- Touch only what you must. Clean up only your own mess.
- Define success criteria. Loop until verified.
- This repo is a **SAT>IP lab server** (Go), not a client app and not a full SAT>IP implementation.
- Lab state: `internal/lab/` (catalog, tuners, sessions); JSON API on HTTP — see `docs/api.md`.
- Run `make test` before claiming work is complete.
- RTSP responses must use `\r\n\r\n` line endings.
- Do not expand scope into full spec or TCP interleaved RTSP without explicit request.
- Update `docs/supported-profile.md` and `docs/api.md` when user-visible simulation or lab API behavior changes.
- Agent branches: `codex/<topic>`.

Quick layout: `cmd/satip-lab` (main), `cmd/satip-lab-smoke`, `internal/{config,channels,lab,httpserver,ssdp,rtsp,ts,simulator,smoke}`.
